{"tid":105267,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白官發言人「另類事實」之言，令《1984》再次大熱","createTime":"2017-02-02T17:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T13:46:50.000Z","uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"98afe28f888d3c717795ff41841308c1f024bbee","tid":105267,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:36:57.000Z","msg":"白宮顧問康韋日前在總統就職觀禮人數的風波上，力撐白宮發言人斯派塞指有關人數是「史上最多」之言，稱對方所言是「另類事實」。康韋此言令各方嘩然，還帶挈英國作家奧威爾（George Orwell）的反極權小說《1984》熱賣，登上亞馬遜暢書排行榜第一位。《1984》在一九四九年首次發行，描述在極權制度下，一切真相都會扭曲。對於今次康韋的「另類事實」論，《華盛頓郵報》記者指就像書中所言：「到最後，黨可以宣布二加二等於五，你還不得不相信它。」<br />\n<br />\n大驚小怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢個講法確係關公災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真有咁多人就事實，<br />\n無就唔係事實，另類事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難關令人聯想到1984既新語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b6f1e895f1c461f271d1e3c4eebf7429e6e56e","tid":105267,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:40:33.000Z","msg":"Old news imgur 一早講完"},{"pid":"a5a3c9c65ba567f65ec571ff1915c8fcba8a892c","tid":105267,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T18:09:48.000Z","msg":"old news is so"},{"pid":"4aa001fd55747b1a35a8835be46700fc58ee6401","tid":105267,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"而家香港70&divide;2=20"}]}